# Empire Bot — n8n Workflow Environment Variables
#
# These workflows reference the bot token via the n8n expression
# {{ $env.TELEGRAM_BOT_TOKEN }} instead of a hardcoded value.
#
# Set this as an environment variable on the n8n instance itself
# (e.g. in the n8n server's .env file, or via docker-compose
# `environment:` / `env_file:` for the n8n container), NOT inside
# the workflow JSON.
#
# Get your token from @BotFather on Telegram.
# NEVER commit the real value — this file is a template only.

TELEGRAM_BOT_TOKEN=your-telegram-bot-token-here
